channel.title: Does anyone have the ID for the Character Interface title?
channel.description:
Hi. I was wondering if anyone has the Interface ID (Or whatever its called - I've forgotten), for the character design interface's title? I was hoping to change it so it doesn't say "Welcome to RuneScape - Use the buttons below to design your character...", because its not RuneScape... I have ran several searches using a for loop which uses sendframe126 on a large amount of IDs, but it doesnt want to find it. :(
Well, if anyone knows, could they please post here. Thanks.
Ben Corbett AKA Unborn
